        {
            "title": "勝宏科技登場高收逾50% 每手賬賺1.05萬元",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">勝宏科技(02476)今日登場，挾著暫時是今年集資規模最大IPO的標籤，首日表現亦未令人失望，高收逾50%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：勝宏科技官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/20260330_FI_source-web_300476.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：勝宏科技官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/20260330_FI_source-web_300476.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：勝宏科技官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">該股收報315元，較招股價209.88元高50.09%；以1手100股計，認購並獲配每手賬面賺1.05萬元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">該股今日全程穩企於招股價之上，低位302元時仍較招股價高43.89%；高位336.2元，更高於招股價60.19%，成交達107.84億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">相反，勝宏科技A股(300476.SZ)今日則全程報跌，收報330.9元人幣，跌3.53%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15900541-%e5%8b%9d%e5%ae%8f%e7%a7%91%e6%8a%80%e7%99%bb%e5%a0%b4%e9%ab%98%e6%94%b6%e9%80%be50-%e6%af%8f%e6%89%8b%e8%b3%ac%e8%b3%ba1-05%e8%90%ac%e5%85%83",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/04/P2026042100315_photo_1326465_FB.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-21 16:30:06",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "全日收市︱升幅略擴 恒指升126點報26487點 傳統藍籌撐市 主板成交不足2100億",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">港股午後升勢稍為提升，以中移動(00941)為首的傳統藍籌合力撐市，但市場亦觀望美伊談判發展，大市成交隨之縮減，主板交投降至2051.77億元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：中國移動官網影片截圖\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20230724_FI_source-web_00941.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中國移動官網影片截圖\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20230724_FI_source-web_00941.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：中國移動官網影片截圖</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒生指數今早高開81點後幾乎全日報升，僅在早市後段短暫倒跌，低位26342點時僅微跌19點，但上升動力也未太足夠，縱使午後重新發力，但高位26529點時也僅升168點，全日波幅不足200點。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒指最後收報26487點，升126點或0.48%。恒生科技指數明顯跑輸，全日大部份時間報跌，收報5061點，跌4點或0.08%；國企指數則升44點或0.5%，報8943點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15900522-%e5%85%a8%e6%97%a5%e6%94%b6%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e5%8d%87%e5%b9%85%e7%95%a5%e6%93%b4-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e5%8d%87126%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b126487%e9%bb%9e-%e5%82%b3%e7%b5%b1%e8%97%8d%e7%b1%8c%e6%92%90%e5%b8%82",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/HKSTOCK-5.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-21 16:19:48",
